         gir1.2-adw-1,
         libadwaita-1-0,
         policykit-1
Description: Native GTK4 front end for Nmap
 Zenmap Native is a Linux graphical front end for the Nmap Security Scanner.
 It is built with GTK 4 and Libadwaita and complements the classic GTK3
 zenmap package. Saved scans and settings are stored under
 ~/.config/zenmap-native/.
